3. Files and Code Sections:
   - **`/Users/bulutyazgan/Desktop/marketify/app/(auth)/signup/lister.tsx`** (CREATED this story, was a stub):
     - Main implementation of US-033. Three-field form + Field sub-component + client validate + submit handler.
